 systems and ecological\ntraps,\" <i>Oikos,</i> <b>103</b>: 457\u2013468</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Patten2-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Patten2_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Patten, M. A., and D. T. Bolger (2003) \"Variation in top-down control of avian reproductive success across a fragmentation gradient\", <i>Oikos,</i> <b>101</b>:479\u2013488</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1327\nCached time: 20180909223241\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.078 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 236/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 757/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 79/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 4790/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.010/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 804 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   44.190      1 Template:Reflist\n100.00%   44.190      1 -total\n 58.66%   25.923      1 Template:Webarchive\n  5.97%    2.638      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:31536987-0!canonical and timestamp 20180909223241 and revision id 847653746\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","hidden":"","*":"Webarchive_template_wayback_links"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Environmental_terminology"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Biology_terminology"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Environmental_conservation"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Ecology"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Landscape_ecology"}],"links":[{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Allee effect"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Clutch size"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Ecological trap"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Ecological traps"},{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Ecology"},{"ns":0,"exists":""